Package: lite-nas-system-metrics
Version: @PACKAGE_VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @PACKAGE_ARCH@
Maintainer: Oleksiy Bondar <bondaroleksiyandroyovich@gmail.com>
Depends: nats-server, openssl, systemd
Description: LiteNAS system metrics service
 Collects system metrics from /proc, publishes them over the local NATS bus,
 and installs the hardened lite-nas-system-metrics systemd service.
